Description: Ichigo Kurosaki sees dead people and must help usher them safely into the afterlife.
Title: BLEACH, VOL. 28
Author: Tite Kubo

Description: Jiraiya, ninja and mentor to Naruto, put everything he learned about the Akatsuki organization in code. Can Naruto decipher it in time?
Title: NARUTO, VOL. 45
Author: Masashi Kishimoto

Description: This series follows Yotsuba, a young girl learning about the world. In this chapter, she recycles, gets a bike and discovers sticky notes. Really.
Title: YOTSUBA&!, VOL. 6
Author: Kiyohiko Azuma

Description: This series, set in the future, is about an online, multiplayer game run amok. This volume concludes the tale.
Title: .HACK G.U.   , VOL. 5
Author: Hamazaki Tatsuya

Description: Two brothers harmed in a ritual that was half magic/half science seek the legendary Philosopher’s Stone to make things right. But others seek the weapon of alchemy for their own nefarious means.
Title: FULLMETAL ALCHEMIST, VOL. 20
Author: Hiromu Arakawa

Description: Cross Academy has day and evening students, but the latter have a secret: they are vampires.
Title: VAMPIRE KNIGHT, VOL. 7
Author: Matsuri Hino

Description: This series is about a family that is possessed by the animals of the Chinese zodiac. Secrets from the past are revealed and Akito, head of the clan, finds her control slipping.
Title: FRUITS BASKET, VOL. 23
Author: Natsuki Takaya

Description: This murder mystery was adapted from a video game. This volume has more deaths and twins battling over Keiichi’s affection.
Title: HIGURASHI: WHEN THEY CRY, VOL. 2
Author: Ryukishi07 and Yutori Houjyou

Description: Misao Harada can see the magic hidden in the world, but it turns out to be a a power that demons wants to exploit. Will her childhood friend, Kyo, who is the head of a demon clan, help or hurt her?
Title: BLACK BIRD, VOL. 1
Author: Kanoko Sakurakoji

Description: Naruto’s former teammate, Sasuke, learns vital details about his family’s past.
Title: NARUTO, VOL. 43
Author: Masashi Kishimoto
